data.description: Embrace the power of prime location! This exquisite condo is a mere half-block away from the U of U campus & a 5 minute drive from downtown Salt Lake City. Within easy walking distance to multiple coffee shops, restaurants, & grocery stores. Convenient public bus access on 100 S. and 200 S. corners of 1300 E. This beautiful condo offers an array of amenities and convenience.  The building features brick and white steel, mid-century modern design that fits the historic area aesthetic.
